data.description: This precious two bedroom ranch-style home is located in East Athenss Emerald Pointe subdivision. Boasting many desirable features, this home offers a convenient garage, vaulted ceilings for an open feel, and wood floors and neutral paint colors for a classic feel. Just inside is the sizable living room with a cozy fireplace and built-in shelving. The eat-in kitchen displays white cabinets, a tile backsplash, stainless steel appliances, and a large eat-in dining area. Just beyond the kitchen is the laundry closet with room for a washer on one side and a dryer on the other with storage shelving above each. Off the back is a terrific screened porch overlooking the private backyard where you can enjoy cool evenings. Both of the bedrooms have carpet flooring, ceiling fans, and ample closet space. This property is located just minutes from the UGA Vet School and all of the shopping and dining that East Athens offers.
